name: SHA

values.name: sha1sum
values.comment:
Takes a string. Produces a sha1sum (string).

    sha1sum "foo æ ø å ñ"
        == "48a24ab372f84906d5f02386f94adf8f00238a9c"

    sha1sum "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog"
        == "2fd4e1c67a2d28fced849ee1bb76e7391b93eb12"
